# Currency Converter - Spring Boot Project

This is a simple Currency Converter web application built using **Spring Boot**, **JSP**, and **Maven**.

## ğŸš€ Features
- Convert currencies using real-time exchange rates
- User-friendly JSP interface
- MVC architecture with Spring Boot

